                            <comment id="13494685" author="aw" created="Sat, 10 Nov 2012 13:36:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;When -m 0 is specified, it should probably just call copy in a serial fashion across the list and not run a MapReduce job.  After all, setting the number of maps to zero implies that one doesn&apos;t want a job executed at all.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
